Collected from the \&quot;Unofficial Wiretap Podcast\&quot;
 &lt;a href=&quot;
http://limelight.collectik.net/collectik/feed/21055&quot; rel=&quot;nofollow&quot; target=&quot;_NEW&quot;&gt;
http://limelight.collectik.net/collectik/feed/21055&lt;/a&gt;

This show is beyond excellent in terms of writing, originality and wit.  I made this torrent to help out other Wiretap fans who are frustrated by the lack of an official podcast.  

While the collection is incomplete and the quality not as good as it could be, it\&amp;#039;s what I could best round up.  

I plan on hopefully creating my own \&quot;unofficial podcast\&quot; in the upcoming weeks at a more listenable bitrate.  

Thanks very much to whoever it was who did originally encode these files though!

